{"tid":2431971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[分化狗冚家剷]重點唔在於走唔走 ok?屌你老母","createTime":"2021-03-04T04:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T06:34:35.000Z","uid":227445,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62263debdc1dc8d708dc97469c110a331159660f","tid":2431971,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:09:09.000Z","msg":"屌人走唔走從來只係偽名題黎<br />\n重點在你走 / 唔走之後會諗乜9做乜9<br />\n走唔代表永世唔返黎 大把野可以做<br />\n而走最值得注意一點係<br />\n你會buy到多好多時間<br />\n無論即刻行動 定 唞下先<br />\n都好可能比stay有多得多既時間去計劃下一步<br />\n<br />\n揀留既當然亦有要注意既<br />\n人生安全基本野<br />\n無論做線人 記錄 安全屋 地下野乜乜乜<br />\n都對可能嚟到既未來有相當影響<br />\n係好危險 但有必要 亦會有用既敵後殿後野<br />\n所以亦唔應該話留既係蠢 有問題 <br />\n<br />\n明知大撚鑊都肯殿後睇晒場戲完場無庸置疑係值得尊敬既<br />\n但唔代表走就一定係懦夫 唔做野<br />\n狡兔三窟 ok? 無計劃咁留低可以仲衰過走佬<br />\n命都無埋玩撚毛<br />\n<br />\n最大問題係你唔知唔諗咁做有咩作用 好處/壞處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1157a6f18fe1044577d4ccc6c9809c603217110","tid":2431971,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:16:22.000Z","msg":"三毛會扮兩邊"},{"pid":"4ed35476ad2e8e10a52b2faf4dc40b0d334358ac","tid":2431971,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T04:53:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又畀班仆街洗走"},{"pid":"86f5486822f4548f98fb095d0bcc18458bf72fbb","tid":2431971,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T05:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c03c1f2873e40c8f5a0f72934b81dd362725fa","tid":2431971,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T10:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你老妹<br />\n洗post真係好恐怖<br />\n互屌放負分化post就鬼咁多頁"},{"pid":"07738f937b6a14bd1a90f9f33d833ac8942fdfc1","tid":2431971,"uid":54927,"lik